---
title: Cheesy Pulled Pork Enchiladas with Tomato Salsa & Greek Yoghurt
description: You're going to fall head over heels for our new pulled pork. With the long slow cooking already done, it's ready to roll  in any recipe. Try adding the juicy, tender meat to a saucy filling, rolling it up in tortillas and baking it with a cheesy crust.  It's enchilada heaven!
